# Modern browsers only - eliminates legacy JavaScript polyfills
# This targets ES2020+ support, significantly reducing bundle size
# and improving TTI scores

# Chrome 88+ (2021)
Chrome >= 88

# Firefox 78+ (2020)
Firefox >= 78

# Safari 14+ (2020)
Safari >= 14

# Edge 88+ (2021)
Edge >= 88

# Mobile Safari iOS 14+
iOS >= 14

# Chrome Mobile 88+
ChromeAndroid >= 88

# Samsung Internet 15+
Samsung >= 15

# Explicitly exclude legacy browsers to force modern transpilation
not IE 11
not Chrome < 88
not Firefox < 78
not Safari < 14
not Edge < 88
not iOS < 14

# Coverage: ~95% of global users (as of 2024)
# Trade-off: Eliminates legacy polyfills for significant performance gains
